name: Calyxia677630_720
description: Calyxia iterates over a grid, centred on zero, using a periodic mathematical function to generate glitchy, repetitive loops. Resolution is intentionally limited to introduce interference effects, but this has been rendered at 720x720 pixels to allow for detail.  The image is further enhanced with slight rotation and post-rendering effects. A seed value is used to create many of the parameters, in this case 677630. The original resolution is available as an edition of 10.
